data.name: label2.Text
data.value:
Regenerates modded files by applying changes handled by auto_patcher to the current game files. This is useful to resolve conflicts with other mods.
Make sure to install mods in the following order: > Restore to vanilla (and delete MEM texture scans) > Install other DLC / content mods > Run this tool > Install LE2 Liara Squadmate > Install texture mods

data.name: autoGrowLabel1.Text
data.value: Location of this mod's CookedPCConsole folder within the mod library, meaning where ME3Tweaks imported the mod, not where the DLC is located in the game files. E.g. E:\ME3Tweaks\LE2\LE2-Liara_Squadmate\DLC_MOD_LiaraSquad\CookedPCConsole
